les from real-life applications, comparing the side effects of low-dose\ntricyclic antidepressants with a placebo, the efficacy of the treatment group\nin a teratological experiment, and the efficiency of the active drugs in curing\ninfection for clinical trials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 16:20:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-05"}
