 show that our model can generate\nimages and tabular data with high fidelity to the causal framework and\naccommodate explicit de-biasing to ignore undesired relationships in the causal\ndata compared to the baseline.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 16:53:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jul 2022 16:18:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 11 Feb 2023 00:04:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-14"}
